data.description: Nice brick, ranch style home on 8+ acres! Home has an open floor plan, 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths. Solar Panels, whole property is fenced, there is a barn on the property as well. Propane & well on property as well. Per seller there are no restrictions on cattle, horses, other animals.
